{
  "stem": "20609.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We didn't keep kosher because we didn't-- we had the store downstairs which was not kosher.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I remember when my father opened up the second store, you know, and I overheard a conversation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He says, nothing is going to happen to us because we got our best customers are the SA.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We had some big shots coming in because we made the finest liver pate in Berlin and we had-- my father used to go to Poland to buy the geese and the chickens because Poland had the quality of-- of poultry.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And so he always was under the impression nothing can happen to him, like so many other Jews in Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was in the Austrian Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't forget, when my father was born, he was born outside of Krakow, Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that time when he was born, it was Austria, Austro-Hungarian Empire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in 1912, two years before the war, he was drafted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when he was ready for discharge, the-- the-- the other war started.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he spent six years in an Austrian regiment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he got discharged in 1918.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was wounded a couple of times.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He showed me once in a while his-- well, he didn't talk that much about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and I believe he came to Germany in 1919, right after-- after the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, we had some family who lived in-- in the, right on the border there, and that's where he used to buy his stuff, in [INAUDIBLE], which is-- which is-- right in-- it's a border city in-- on the Polish side, which at one time was German or something like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So-- so that's where he-- because his family was in the wholesale business with poultry and things like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
